data.description:
Welcome Home! From the peaceful ambiance of the front porch to the quiet tree filled back yard, this home is a wonderful place to call home! Step into an open airy atmosphere with an abundance of natural light. This home includes a formal living area perfect for entertaining. The eat-in kitchen includes a spacious pantry overlooking the family room with a cozy fireplace creating a welcoming and inviting space for the whole family to enjoy. Step out onto your deck in your private backyard for a serene and relaxing getaway where you can unwind, entertain guests, or simply enjoy the natural surroundings. Some updating has been done including Luxury vinyl planking throughout the lower levels, new concrete driveway and front stoop. Roof, to be replaced and back porch to be painted. This delightful home is a pleasure to show and is move-in ready!
Buyer's agent to verify all square footage, taxes, permits, schools and all listing information. Listing agent related to the seller.
